This paper deals with optimising reasoning in OWL 2 RL systems, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence applications. The paper also discusses efficiency and correctness, which are important considerations in database systems (cs.DB) and logic (cs.LO). Additionally, the paper presents an algorithm, which falls under the category of deep learning (cs.DL) and software engineering (cs.SE).
